/******************************************************************************    
** Name:     UPS_SIT_GetSummaryOfCashTransaction    
** Short Desc: Get Error details from table 'TBL_SIT_EBRSummaryOfCashTransaction'.      
**    
** Full Description : Get Error details from table 'TBL_SIT_EBRSummaryOfCashTransaction'.  
**            
